begin="37.580" end="39.952" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.580" end="37.769">Think</span> <span begin="37.769" end="38.019">we</span> <span begin="38.019" end="38.239">were</span> <span begin="38.239" end="38.453">bet</span><span begin="38.453" end="38.657">ter</span> <span begin="38.657" end="39.139">off</span> <span begin="39.139" end="39.314">so</span><span begin="39.314" end="39.952">lo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我想我们都孤身一人更好</span></p><p begin="42.030" end="45.347" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="42.030" end="42.240">I</span> <span begin="42.240" end="42.402">got</span> <span begin="42.402" end="42.649">that</span> <span begin="42.649" end="43.022">act</span> <span begin="43.022" end="43.382">right</span> <span begin="43.382" end="43.459">in</span> <span begin="43.459" end="43.620">the</span> <span begin="43.620" end="43.782">Win</span><span begin="43.782" end="43.980">dy</span> <span begin="43.980" end="44.194">ci</span><span begin="44.194" end="44.410">ty</span> <span begin="44.410" end="44.742">that</span> <span begin="44.742" end="45.347">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在大风肆虐的芝加哥夜晚 我们缱绻不眠(Windy City指芝加哥)</span></p><p begin="45.347" end="46.980" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="45.347" end="45.553">No</span> <span begin="45.553" end="45.990">trees</span> <span begin="45.990" end="46.176">to</span> <span begin="46.176" end="46.530">blow</span> <span begin="46.530" end="46.980">through</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">大麻已经抽尽</span></p><p begin="46.982" end="48.681" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="46.982" end="47.187">But</span> <span begin="47.187" end="47.504">blow</span> <span begin="47.504" end="47.779">me</span> <span begin="47.779" end="47.886">and</span> <span begin="47.886" end="48.061">I</span> <span begin="48.061" end="48.362">owe</span> <span begin="48.362" end="48.681">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh