/span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">啊，呜</span></span></p><p begin="3:27.466" end="3:28.746" itunes:key="L54" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:27.466" end="3:27.757">So</span><span begin="3:27.757" end="3:28.620">lo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一个人孤单失落</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="3:27.234" end="3:28.746"><span begin="3:27.234" end="3:28.746">(Ooh)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">呜</span></span></p><p begin="3:28.911" end="3:29.584" itunes:key="L55" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:28.911" end="3:29.107">By</span> <span begin="3:29.107" end="3:29.288">my</span><span begin="3:29.288" end="3:29.584">self</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只有我一个人</span></p><p begin="3:30.991" end="3:35.684" itunes:key="L56" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:30.991" end="3:31.339">So</span><span begin="3:31.339" end="3:32.315">lo,</span> <span begin="3:34.673" end="3:34.907">so</span><span begin="3:34.907" end="3:35.684">lo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一个人低落 一个人生活</span></p><p begin="3:38.190" end="3:45.135" itunes:key="L57" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:38.190" end="3:38.457">So</span><span begin="3:38.457" end="3:39.284">lo,</span> <span begin="3:41.730" end="3:42.026">so</span><span begin="3:42.026" end="3:42.883">lo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只有一个人 一个人</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="3:42.293" end="3:45.135"><span begin="3:42.293" end="3:45.135">(Ooh)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">呜</span></span></p><p begin="3:45.222" end="3:46.409" itunes:key="L58" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:45.222" end="3:45.519">So</span><span begin="3:45.519" end="3:46.409">lo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一个人</span></p></div></body></tt>